 Cell[BoxData["\"\<estimator\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
  "60656f21-600c-4cf7-ad0d-8a057cb43f50"],
 " job with an observable instead of a sampler job. The observable is laid \
out onto the transpiled circuit, so a 3-qubit ",
 Cell[BoxData["\"\<ZZZ\>\""], "InlineFormula",ExpressionUUID->
  "5c607660-d6fe-4005-8582-67a35b7820c4"],
 " is accepted against a many-qubit backend:"
}], "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"f1d021f1-ed7c-49c8-81d2-68a2651a0cf3"],

